  <brief_title>A Comparative Study of the Efficacy of Penciclovir 10mg/g (1%) Cream in Preventing the Appearance of Classical Lesion in Recurrent Cold Sore Sufferers</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised, Double-blind, Vehicle Controlled, Single Center, Parallel Group, Comparative Study of the Efficacy of Penciclovir 10mg/g (1%) Cream in Preventing the Appearance of Classical Lesion in Recurrent Cold Sore Sufferers</official_title>
