  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of the efficacy of penciclovir 10 mg/g (1%) cream with that of vehicle at 72 hours
      in preventing the appearance of classical lesions following prodromal symptoms (tingling or
      burning sensation) based on thermographic assessment among recurrent cold sore sufferers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
